# Screenshots are big and regeneratable from the flow. Gitignored by default.
# If a specific test folder needs its screenshots committed (e.g. a reference
# set for visual regression, or a finalized guide getting handed off), opt in
# by adding a `!<test-slug>/screenshots/` line below.
**/screenshots/

# Allow the smoke screenshots so a fresh clone has a reference of what a
# working first run looks like.
!_smoke/screenshots/

# Local PDF exports (auto-generated from .md by Markdown PDF VSCode extension
# or similar). The .md is the source of truth; PDFs are per-machine.
**/*.pdf
